com.facebook.buck.apple

Class XcodeRuleConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.apple.XcodeRuleConfiguration

  • public class XcodeRuleConfiguration
extends Object
    Represents a layered Xcode build configuration. The first layer is the lowest layer on the list, that is, the latter layers are visited first when resolving variables.

      • fromRawJsonStructure

        public static ImmutableSet<XcodeRuleConfiguration> fromRawJsonStructure(ImmutableMap<String,ImmutableList<Either<Path,ImmutableMap<String,String>>>> configurations)
        Convert from a raw json representation of the Configuration to an actual Configuration object.
        Parameters:
        configurations - A map of configuration names to lists, where each each element is a layer of the configuration. Each layer can be specified as a path to a .xcconfig file, or a dictionary of xcode build settings.
